  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1995330/extras/77a298737209bc33fc052ef94eb2b47b.webp?t=1771068203\" width=511 height=50 /></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>The twist? The action takes place on a tower that evolves continuously!  <br></li><li>Different types of weapons await you, each useful in different situations!<br></li><li>Release magical powers on enemies that climb on the tower.<br></li><li>Evolve your tower every 10 waves and choose new passives with your upgrade coins!</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1995330/extras/e581981784fb04dfd1420ea1dac8e6e7.poster.avif?t=1771068203\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1995330/extras/e581981784fb04dfd1420ea1dac8e6e7.webm?t=1771068203\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1995330/extras/e581981784fb04dfd1420ea1dac8e6e7.mp4?t=1771068203\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1995330/extras/7cf75d3c78e3b5437b1be4c72e3689b0.webp?t=1771068203\" width=317 height=51 /></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Defeat the enemies trying to reach the crystal at the top of the tower!<br></li><li>Each enemy one has its own behavior!<br></li><li>Pick the right weapons and powers to defeat them!</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1995330/extras/4a82b27161b0550127205002a20f9575.poster.avif?t=1771068203\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1995330/extras/4a82b27161b0550127205002a20f9575.webm?t=1771068203\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1995330/extras/4a82b27161b0550127205002a20f9575.mp4?t=1771068203\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1995330/extras/a37c7c67868063b56e8c50c7ef18c3b3.webp?t=1771068203\" width=361 height=50 /></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Challenge yourself after beating the main game!<br></li><li>Unlock the hardest difficulty after 100 waves!<br></li><li>Enjoy tower defense awesomeness in endless mode!<br></li><li>Randomized waves and enemies will keep you on your toes!</li></ul>",
